description: Feelin' brave? You don't always have to use the Insane Bravery Stratagem! Sometimes discretion really is the better part of valour.

title: How To Paint: Battle Ready Tyranid Neurotyrant and Neuroloids
description:
The Neurotyrant is an immensely powerful psychic creature, projecting a Shadow in the Warp that drives its prey to screaming madness. In this guide we'll be showing you how to paint a Tyranid Neurotyrant and one of its accompanying Neuroloids relays to Battle Ready. 

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it

Don't forget to like, share and subscribe and to ring the bell to make sure you keep up to date with all our latest videos!

title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Ultramarines Captain in Terminator Armour
description:
Equipped with powerful Terminator armour, this Ultramarines Captain fights from the front. In this guide, we'll be showing you how to get this miniature painted quickly and easily, ready to deploy by teleport strike straight onto the gaming table.  

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it
